Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When i was a kid,\Nin a crazy dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,i was gazin' up to\Nthe promised land
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らのユメの形　ザワメキ出す heart！ beat！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,come on let's go to that place
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,i just can't stop anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛びだせ　仄暗い空　fly into the light
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じたいこの世界に生まれたことが幸せってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新時代へ続く扉を開けるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wow wow oh oh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なぁ、わかってるんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らはいつだって傷だらけで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しみのルーツ断ち切って
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怖くないよ　いつでも傍に感じるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから　もっと　もっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱い　力が心満たしてく
